extendedInfo.description: This is an app that shows the song list for each Rock Band game.View songlists for each gameSearch for songs & artistsSort Songs ListsGet Video/Lyric ResultsSave songs to a list, add scoresDLC - 17/03/13RBN - 17/03/13

reviews.title: Almost there
reviews.comment: Thanks for updating this handy app! There are a couple of reasons why I\'m not giving it a 5-Star rating yet: The list of games is duplicated, and when you search for a song, the search results are also duplicated.  I\'d also like to see the most-recent track packs added, like Country Track Pack 2 and Rock Band Blitz.  Will re-rate a 5 if those issues can be addressed.  Overall, though, good app.  Being able to search for a particular song amongst the thousands available as DLC is my favorite feature here.
reviews.author: Matt Birchall
